I'd move this code into your resetPermissions function body. You do this by waiting on the updateComplete promise.
this.updateComplete.then(() => {
let inputs = this.renderRoot.querySelectorAll("input[type='checkbox']");
inputs.forEach(elem => {
let role = elem.getAttribute('data-role');
let perm = elem.getAttribute('data-perm');
  if (role && perm) {
    elem.checked = this.on[role].includes(perm);
  }
})

});
... you get the idea. That way the  render has finished and you can manipulate the checks.

